  "text": "The overall goal of our experiments is to examine the speedup of our token account solutions relative to the baseline proactive implementations, while keeping the same overall communication rate. In order to evaluate our protocols, we ran simulation experiments using the PeerSim simulation environment [CITATION_1] . Since one of our main targeted application domain is smartphone networks, our experimental scenarios include a real smartphone trace as well with realistic availability and churn patterns.",
